i quit my shitty jobs at pier 1 and shaws. worked in hyannis temporarily. my birthday wasn't very eventful but the day after theresa, jen, shelly, and i all went to castaways. jen was trashed. cindy showed herself..lol jen was bashing on her hard..she had to have heard she was like a foot away! 

pac sun hired me. yay! 

my car needs a sponge bath..someone wash it for me!

so whos the lame ass that called me immature in a comment on MY journal? i really dont care. ;] im so fucking happy! i met this kid matt that drives an ambulance. fucking emt wants to be my man. ;D now the question is do i really want a relationship. i dont know. i thought i did. im just sick of wasting time on guys that will keep me happy for a few years and than i have to kick them out of my life forever cuz they end up sucking. relationships..go figure

Theresa, mike, timmy, n andy all drove up to dave n busters together. i got to sit between the two boys that couldn't stop beating on each other. my head was between my legs half the time and the other half i was on top of andy. it was jess' b-day. ;] i slept on mikes couch. his dog is so big...tex loves me. were all going to her house tonight to party some more! i was suppose to work at shaws but fuck it. ill just tell them im working at pier 1. theresa wants me to move in with her and mike. i need to pay off the one bill i have first. i'd rather not live at home..i dont mind it but ya know. im over the boyfriend idea. i just want a guy i can hang with that will fucking treat me nice. ;] got a few in mind..haha im over falling in love. i wanna fall in like. theresa, mike, n i went out for breakfast. im on a coffee high now. theresa n i were getting guys to give us there tickets..sooo fucking funny! i gotta go clean the dirtyness of last night off me..kidding! but seriously... it's hard to say how i feel today for years gone by...and i cryed. since you've been gone it's not the same.

tubing was fun on sunday. kristin is silly. i worked at shaws today..it was so easy. i have to comment about saturday with theresa again...i was so0o0o happy! the first/only boy i wanted to kiss...kissed me and i just talked to him on the phone. muhahaha...what a fucking good time.i dont know how the hell i drove home though..bad. i do remember driving by a state trooper..very bad. there was this really good band playing some awesome 80's songs at the bar in boston. your damn right i knew all the lyrics. pppfftt.. i may not remember what happened to my money.. or who was dancing behind me at some point but i remember dancing to this song.. i dont mind you coming here wasting all my time cuz when your standing oh so near i kind of lose my mind i dont mind you hanging out and talking in your sleep i guess your just what i needed i needed someone to please

last night i went to theresa's! ;D we went on a party bus up to boston. the jello shots kicked my ass. there was this cute boy that i talked to and than..i made out with a cute guy..with a kick ass tat. now im on my way to go tubing...thanks daddy ;]

i went to the sky bar in boston last night. good times with theresa! <33

your tolerance wrong

apologies are breaking me

for two days i wait for calls to come through

i went to shelby woo's last night. we always have a million laughs. were gonna go to school in september. i have to. i dont want to work retail the rest of my life. if i had just gone when i got out of high school i could have a job right now where i could support myself. oh well...ill blame that on me. i just called noah. he makes me giggle. i forgot to write about him in here. he was the cute boy that kissed me goodbye at the airport. made me laugh and kept me company when i was living with mckenna for the last week. i think he just made it so much easier for me to leave hawaii without saying goodbye to james. i think i already thanked him but i should do it again next time i talk to him. he's also an awesome fucking guitar player. <3 musicians are always sexy. haha...i think ima head down to shelly's in a bit. i dont work until wednesday...i've been bored. thursday i have to work at the hanover pier 1. gay.

i went to the doctor friday. the doctor was nice. the med's i just started taking made my tummy hurt last night. than today i just felt weird, tingly, and dizzy. <s>i <3 jimi</s> im bored..

you dont know who i am

Echo

Mexico

11 AM

yesterday morning at 7:10 i woke up like 1/2 way when ur not really awake. than all of a sudden the whole freakin island of oahu started shaking for like 45 seconds! my kittie ran to me. a few seconds after it stopped there was a lil aftershock. i was waiting for it to really start shakeing and that would be the last anyone had heard from the girl that went to live in hawaii for a bit. i heard the power go off right after. yes i HEARD it. zzoooppp. like when a robot shuts down..silly. james went to work. im use to being in mass and figured the electricity wouldnt be out for more than a few hours so i told him to take the car. after waking up all sweaty a few times to check if the power is on yet, i finally decide i cant sleep through the power being out anymore. i get up and dont know what the hell im going to do with myself. i trying calling shelly to tell her im alive. my fucking cell phone wont work...at all. after playing with the fuse box to make sure im not just a stupid girl that cant figure out how to turn the power on i went for a walk outside. two boys stopped me and said their power was out and their cell's werent working. it was like the world had ended outside, or as close as ive ever seen it. all the stores were closed or blocked off. all the traffic lights n crosswalk signals were out..hence the no power on the island. james comes home and saves me at like 4pm. there was no power in waikiki at all. sucks for all the people on vacation. no planes were departing from the island. when james got home we were almost out of gas and figured we had just enough to get where the power had just turned back on in pearlridge/aiea. the lines to get gas were all the way down the road. we only sat there for like 20 mins waiting. we needed food! all the fast food places had lines from the drive thru to like a mile down the road. it was crazy! damn people come on now its only been 10 hours without fast food! james and i went to walmart..it was fucking crazy..well walmarts always crazy but i mean it was like a mosh pit without the music. shitty. i grabbed some cheetos and we got the fuck out of there! ;D all i heard all morning was sirens...i didnt give a shit at the time though..i was trying to sleep without a/c. james and i got back on the highway..going "lights!!" ..."no lights" hopeing that we wouldnt have to amuse ourselves by candle light. well i would amuse myself and he would go to sleep. stupid boy. we get off our exit as i scream "no lights!!". i lite the candles when we got home...james tryed to go to sleep. about an hour later i hear what sounds like a bunch of hoodlems screaming. i thought about how imature the stupid kids were for being so loud when it was late and after everything that had happened. than we got power back is was around like 8:30. than i realized im a bitch b/c the people were just yelling cuz they got power back..duh lyndz. the apartments across the street were out for about an hour or so more. haha! ;X the whole day i was thinking fuck..something worth telling everyone about and i cant fucking call anyone. i didnt know what the hell had happened until james came and we listened to the radio the whole way. his store didnt even open he sat outside from 9-3:30 with everyone seeing if the power was going to come on. i didnt have to work yesterday..or today so i wasnt even thinking about champs sports. 6.6 magnatidue earthquake off the coast of the big island (hilo). now i've experienced an earthquake, kick ass! the real report today me standing on the jetti at waikiki beach diamond head take me to paradise

;D my camera phone may suck but my sneakers are fucking pretty! i returned my crappy shoes that i had for a month n the nike symbol was peelin' off..defected crap! i got flip-flops, tshirts, sockz, and those pretty sneakers right there! for like $85. i only had to pay .50 after the merc-card for my old shoes i had. i gotta go get dressed again im getting taken to the cheesecake factory in waikiki. i havent been yet. happy friday the 13th!! wo0t! xoxo
I'm glad that you can forgive. I'm only hoping as time goes, you can forget. If it makes you less sad, I'll move out of the state. You can keep to yourself. I'll keep out of your way. ;[ -lyndz

it makes me sad everytime i talk to my mother. all i hear is "when are u coming home?" as happy as i would like to make her by saying today im not leaving...yet. i miss my car! granted i get to drive a nicer new car with leather seats but it's not my car. my poor honda sitting in mass. i know when i leave here and get back to mass im going to be like "why did i leave hawaii?", but than ill just drive over to shelly's. cant fucking drive over to shelly's from this crazy island. fucking pacific ocean. another gorgeous day in hawaii. i miss my thunder and lightning! theres this whole crazy year thats gone by and it feels like its only been one summer. now im going outside to stare at the palm trees..ill miss nights like this when im back home.
this is what my drive to work looks like kaneohe hi - pali lookout jealous?

brian! what email address are you using cuz i have so sent u emails and where are my replies? lyndzfalsereality@yahoo.com is mine silly! since this is the only way you contact me i figured id write you on here. stars are crazy. im moving to a new apartment closer to my job. away from the island traffic. you man you replaceing the floor? email me! <33 -huggies- p.s. im going to see tool tomorrow night!!@!@#@#$
why should i deal with a guy that will only hug me when i cry somtimes..compared to all the time.
what am i suppose to do. ive believed every word before. why should i  do it again? sit here and give it all only to regret it an a few months or a year? whats the point.

as much as i want to go home sometime next year. im glad i came to hawaii. as much as every day i miss everyone and everything. im still glad im here. even after my mother had a stroke right after i left. it feels wrong to be so far away. weird..i know..im in hawaii! i dont know what i want. never have...

my birthday was the best ive ever had. jun 7th went to top of waikiki..which is a rotateing resturant above all the action. it was just great. we went to a bar called mai tai's before we went out to eat. james got me the necklace i wanted. hawaiian jewelry is pretty and kinda unique. i might right more later but it was fucking awesome! ;D

james and i took kittie to the vet today. he acted like a concerned daddy. it was funny!
<font color=deeppink><333

james birthdaywas the 20th we went to ruby tuesdays. i bought him a cake and sang happy birthday. we saw the davinci code. i liked it..very interesting. champs sports had there audit..my manager was so pissed cuz there missing 35,000 dollars of merchandise. shitty. james and i laid in the sun and went swimming today before he went to work. when he left i went and got steak n yummies to make him for dinner. now its cold though..and im hungry waiting for him to get home. james is 25 now! oui i dont even really like the fact that im going to be 21 in a few weeks.besides the being able to buy my own alcohol. oh..well

i work with some crazy people. it seems like a fit right in...odd. my jobs great..so far. i miss mass though. i want to go home so bad..but than i kinda dont. weird eh? i know!! ohh yeah mcdonalds in hawaii serves spam for breakfast! spam is like the greatest think down here..weird. also theres a thing called a bubble drink. its like a milkshake but it has these flavorless gummi balls in it..also weird. jack in the box kicks mcdonalds ass any day and they should be everywhere..or at least mass. no one down here knows what crab ragoon is!! its chinesse food?! or so they say..  i can hear my carver high education sounding a lot better than the way some hawaiians speak. they call is pigeon. instead of i went to the pool, are you going to the pool, or do you want to go to the pool.. it's "go pool" it's funny when i say "what?!" 5 times before i figure out what there saying..it's usually fast, short, and missing a few letters. not like my r's in certain words have appeared anymore than usual. can you tell im bored? james' computer which has cable on it is not woking so this and itunes is my only form of entertainment for i dont know how long.. he just went to work. hes trying to be a life insurance agent of something. this is the first time im home by myself. ;] i came home from work the other day to him in a suit with flowers and a card for me.. yeah thats right he fucked up. i said u cant just buy me flowers..your not forgiven yet but it sure helps your case. i layed at the pool all afternoon no one from the apt complex was there cuz its monday and they get to go to work. ;] james looks like clifford the big red dog after being outside for 2 hours with no sunscreen.  2 more weeks and ill have been in hawaii for 6 months. it doesnt seem like its been that long. crazy..

i just got a better job! better pay..wo0 ho0! its only like 20 mins away. ho0ray! i can be happy again. i got my bacardi 151 to celebrate. o0o yeah. i believe my stupid army roommate/ x friend just ditched us. no shock to me. really evil though. just another person i can add to my list of bullshitters though. ohh yeah im working at champs assistant manager wo0 ho0. they train you to become a manager..he said if i ever want to go home theres plenty of stores there that i could transfer to. yay! im a happy drunk tonight unlike my last post...haha. my mom said when i come back tell james hes not allowed to stay in hawaii by himself. he has to come back with me. ;P his mom said if anything bad happens we can move to maine. he said the last place he would go is maine. im not to fond of it either. yeah hawaii isnt for me they talk funny here..lol beatuiful state but its not home.

As you've no doubt realized over the past week or so, no matter how much you'd like it to, love doesn't run on a schedule -- especially not this kind of love. You've found someone who's really, really appealing to your intellect and your brain -- as well as to your eyes. Who's to say how it will end? Only the two of you. If you're smart, do what you can to make sure the evening ends with a lovely, romantic kiss. funny how this horscope is such bull shit..yet on days in the past it was perfect. i think im dumb i really dont mind work. i meet some great people. some people can just talk to me and go "your from the northeast" its kool i feel special. met this girl the other night from boston she said shed take me out n gave me her email. i love the people from australia. there all so nice...maybe its cuz they're on vacation though. ;X i cant wait to go home on vacation. its gonna be so weird, cool, and sad. i miss shelly. i hate that we dont talk like we use to. i know were 5 hours apart on time. not like i ALWAYS have time to call her but..its just weird not talk to her all the time. ;/ <3333lyndz

spent vday on the beach. the boys made a lil picinic. it was very cute. got ice cream at dole. also got a yummy dinner at home. mm shrimp n chicken. ;] watched saw 2...weird ending. now im watching spongebob. wo0t! a great v-day! xoxo

im being waited on only because im not allowed to go in the living room or kitchen. haha this will never happen again. ;] i dont know what there doing but i know there cooking. ;] i thought they might do something kinda special for me. valentines day is a girls holiday any way. <333 so if your v-day sucks..im sorry. happy v-day anyway. lets see how much more i can drink.'[8
WK$^&&&&&&&&&&&&&&>4wdza   <--kittie trying to lay on the laptop. i got a computer built for me last night. hooray! in all of 15 minutes it was up n running. wo0t my roomies car came finally. <333 i made my journal pretty. <33 john!!  <3333 i cant wait to get some pictures on here. <333

vday is soon. as much as i say i hate the holiday it doesn't really bother me much. my kitty is on my lap. ;] i havent been to work since last sunday. i called in on friday. thats what hapens when you say your only gonna have one drink the night before...among other things. i had school for a few days to get me away from macys. clinique is fun stuff..har har! hopefully my roomies car will be ready tomorrow..its such bull shit! i feel bad for all you suckas in the snow...im sitting here being cold with the a/c on. ;X <333

my daddy had to get my mommy rushed to the hospital a few nights ago. ;[ i've had some clinique training at this nice hotel in waikiki. mm..good food. last class is tomorrow. my roomies car is here its just mixed in with a million other cars..blah. my kitten ia happy though. ;] that makes me happy. so it's all good. i miss shelby woo. my mommy will be okay i think. ive called her like everyday twice since she went was in the hospital. i know if i need to go home i could and i'd even be able to get my ass back to hawaii. <3 these months are going by so fast. its kinda scaring me..im gonna be old. eek june is coming so fast. we went to the cultural center yesterday. it was bomb. hula dancers.. fire show..some hot hula guy..mhm. we saw a pretty imax show. went to luau. o.0 i got laid ;X hehe. well ima go cuz my internet is being a lil stupid.  <3333
did i forget to write in here that i saw nin on nov 14th? the day night before i left mass. did i? well if i did it was fucking great!

i just made this since all the cool girls in cosmetics play on it ;D <3

my space my mother had a small stroke a few days ago. ;[ she was at work. im sad cuz im so far away and my parents are getting older. ;[ my poor mommy. -tear- its just so much nicer here. its not like i want to go back...i hope i dont eat these words later. ;/ im bored i have to work early tomorrow. bleh. kittie is laying on her condo at the moment..yeah you better use that kittie condo bitch i paid for that shit. hehe. shelly hasnt called me in like 4 days. le sigh...oh well ima go play or something. <33

Hello! We moved to Ewa Beach which even though you say it Eva Beach but whatever. I got a cute lil black kitten. My job rocks. Its so cool to live in Hawaii. People are always like "We went on vacation to Hawaii" "We spent are honeymoon in Hawaii". Im like I live here biatch. I miss Shelly. ;[ AlL the girls i work with are funny. Passes the time. I get $260 every like 3-6 months to spend on clinique products. Bomb..free make-up. My baby (linokaee, i cant spell) is sleeping on my roomies spongebob blanket. ;] my dad sent me a john lennon book which i have surprisingly read half of. wo0t go me. i dont remember the last book i...oh yeah i do n/m. ewa beach is beautiful. i almost forgot the best part. Yesterday we went on a hike up a mountain took us like 2 or 3 hours. We get to the waterfall. We head back down the mountain. It starts to get dark. James is holding my hand cuz he cant see. I'm stumbling all over the place. Alfred is using his camera flash as a flash light. Fucking funny! We go the wrong end up in this big field. Turn around get to the end almost. Alfred flashes the path. James is like theres a guy other there we climb down. Book it! Stop running start flashing behind us. Alfred is like my camera is tracking something moving behind us. We see the fence to get out and all make a run for it. FUCK THAT! omg..lol i wish i still smoked weed only b/c i would have hada lighter on me..lmfao. what a reason. What kind of person stands in the pitch black and dosent say anything..omg it was scarey..lol. We got some good pics though when it wasnt dark. We went on a hike last week also. I got really dirty and slipt on my ass like 3 times. Stupid walmart water shoes with no tracktion. I jumper like 100ft of this waterfall. I only looked down for a second and just jumped. James was up there for like 15 mins. He says "You jump first so I dont jump and than you find out you cant." ROFL! Im sure youve all seen a picture of hawaii well it so different to actually be here. <333333 MISS YOU KRISTIN ;]

i am a clinique counter manager. ohh yeah. i get commission for everything i sell!  fuck filees up the ass. i love macys. hawaii takes out like 9% in taxes.  my job at filenes sucked so hard. i was doing all that manual labor and now i get to make people pretty, check sales daily, add a few numbers together, and have the word manager actually be in my title. no more im a LEAD at filenes. lead = you can work as hard as the manager and be a pee on. HI KRISTIN!! i had a dream about an x bf :coughjoncough: last week. i checked my voicemail of the cell i use to own that my dad has yet to cancel and he left me a voicemail. :] my time difference is like 5 hours off though so its hard for me to call anyone. i miss my kittie cats. i believe james is getting me one for xmas..but im trying not to get hopes up since we didnt get the house we were originally planing on. now we are looking at some really classy places. mmhmm...i just need to meet a nice guy to love me now..guys down here are so funny though. they holla at you but for some reason its not disrespectful its just amusing. i went swimming in the beautiful blue ocean 2 days ago. oh yeah i got some more color too. my legs arnt pastey white anymore. go me! some guy actually stopped me on the street today and goes are you from the east coast? i said yeah. and he goes boston? than says he and a group of patriots fans go bar hoppin and wanted me to go tonight. to bad im not 21. bummer. i think maybe i should change my location on n my user info so it will say the right time. well its only 12:30 here now so im gonna go for a walk..wo0t  love n miss my friends n family in mass xoxo
